## Findings

- Wireshark enables deep traffic analysis across OSI layers.
- Navigation and filtering streamline large captures.
- Marking, commenting, and exporting improve collaboration.
- Expert Info provides anomaly hints but requires analyst validation.

## Mitigation / Best Practices

- Use capture filters to reduce noise.
- Apply permanent coloring rules for critical events.
- Document findings with persistent comments.
- Export only relevant traffic for focused analysis.
- Validate Expert Info before acting.
- Set time format to UTC for accurate correlation.

